bills.name: Captain Bill Murray
bills.catchphrase: I'm a nut, but not just a nut.

bills.name: Bill Murray Tangled
bills.catchphrase: And I don't like to work. I only like working when I'm working.

bills.name: Squinting Bill Murray
bills.catchphrase: People say I'm difficult and sometimes that's a badge of honour.

bills.name: Supportive Bill Murray
bills.catchphrase: Don't think about your errors or failures; otherwise, you'll never do a thing.

bills.name: Bill Murray is Over It
bills.catchphrase: I don't want to have a relationship with someone if I'm not going to work with them.

bills.name: Bill Murray Monochrome
bills.catchphrase: Sometimes I snore, like when I get really tired.

bills.name: Classy Bill
bills.catchphrase: Movie acting suits me because I only need to be good for ninety seconds at a time.

bills.name: Just Bill Murray
bills.catchphrase: One of the things I like about acting is that, in a funny way, I come back to myself.

bills.name: Bill Sushi
bills.catchphrase: Yeah, I think that's sort of the American way. And it's also the Polish way, it turns out.
